===Noun===
{{wikipediapar|Inflammation}}
'''inflammation'''

#The act of [[inflame|inflaming]], [[kindle|kindling]], or setting on [[fire]]; also, the state of being inflamed.
#A [[morbid]] condition of any part of the body, consisting in [[congestion]] of the [[blood vessel]]s, with obstruction of the blood current, and growth of morbid [[tissue]]. It is [[manifest]]ed outwardly by redness and swelling, attended with heat and pain.
#Violent [[excitement]]; heat; passion; animosity; turbulence; as, an inflammation of the mind, of the body politic, or of parties.

